document_data.Notable Locations:
Westphal was host to a number of seedy taverns and festhalls, catering to the needs of visiting Amnian sailors.
* [[Caer Westphal]], a fortified castle inhabited by the city's rulers.{{Cite dungeon/196/Backdrop: The Moonshae Isles|12-13}}
* [[Singing Fisherman]], a rundown Ffolk style inn.{{Cite organized play/LFR/Black Heart|13}}
